quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"May both hands of Abu Lahab be ruined, and are ruined are they"
  111,2,"His wealth has not availed him, nor his gains"
  111,3,He will enter a flaming Fire to roast
  111,4,"And (with him) his wife, carrier of firewood (and of evil tales and slander)"
  111,5,Around her neck will be a halter of strongly twisted rope